Package: climecol
Title: What the Package Does (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Joseph", "Baafi", , "jbaafi@mun.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions for archiving, cleaning, analyzing, and 
    visualizing weather and climate data with applications to ecological 
    and infectious disease modeling. Includes utilities for preparing data, 
    fitting periodic functions, and generating inputs for climate-driven models.
